  <section class="section">
    <div class="container" style="max-width:760px;">
      <div class="kicker">Legal</div>
      <h1 class="h1">Privacy</h1>

      <div class="card" style="padding:18px; margin-top:18px;">
        <h2 class="h2">Controller</h2>
        <p class="p"><strong>Domenico Recchia</strong>, 6042 Dietwil, Aargau, Switzerland</p>
        <p class="p">Contact: via the <a href="/en/contact/" style="text-decoration:underline;">contact form</a></p>
      </div>

      <div class="card" style="padding:18px; margin-top:14px;">
        <h2 class="h2">What data is processed?</h2>
        <p class="p">
          If you use the contact form, the information you enter is processed (e.g., name, email, message,
          and optional fields such as company/phone/budget/timeline).
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="card" style="padding:18px; margin-top:14px;">
        <h2 class="h2">Purpose</h2>
        <p class="p">
          Handling your inquiry, communication, and preparing a proposal. No tracking/analytics is used.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="card" style="padding:18px; margin-top:14px;">
        <h2 class="h2">Service providers / hosting</h2>
        <p class="p">
          This website is hosted on Netlify. Forms may be processed via Netlify Forms.
          Form submissions are transmitted to Netlify to deliver your request.
        </p>
        <p class="p">
          In addition, server-side logs (e.g., IP address, timestamp, user agent) may be processed to ensure operations
          and to prevent abuse.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="card" style="padding:18px; margin-top:14px;">
        <h2 class="h2">Retention</h2>
        <p class="p">
          Inquiries are generally retained as long as necessary to handle the request and enable reasonable follow-up
          (typically up to 12 months), unless longer statutory retention obligations apply.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="card" style="padding:18px; margin-top:14px;">
        <h2 class="h2">Fonts / external resources</h2>
        <p class="p">
          Google Fonts are currently loaded. This may result in data being transmitted to Google.
          More information: <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" style="text-decoration:underline;">Google Privacy Policy</a>.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="card" style="padding:18px; margin-top:14px;">
        <h2 class="h2">Your rights</h2>
        <p class="p">
          You may request access, correction, or deletion of your data, as permitted by applicable law.
          Please use the contact form.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
